{"tid":881992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本最辣摔角選手 「超凸出」身材讓網友凍未條！","createTime":"2018-10-30T00:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T05:10:04.000Z","uid":32511,"like":401,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"7bde145668ad6876c6aff713f6b2b4bb308236e9","tid":881992,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:57:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/085530_0cc1c1f34a4cb58a59293ef088bc3292.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F085530_0cc1c1f34a4cb58a59293ef088bc3292.png&h=c7317e16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大部分人對於摔角的印象，應該都是兩個男選手在擂台上進行較量，先將對方給壓制住的另一方就獲勝，但日本近來也積極發展女子摔角，其中一名女摔角手便在推特上引起討論，因為她的身材實在是太火辣了！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/085558_c47fd86095263bb52fc49a1a690acf03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F085558_c47fd86095263bb52fc49a1a690acf03.png&h=6cc8f682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這名女摔角手叫做上福雪，本名上福佑季，是出生於日本神奈川縣的海歸子女，從小在美國生活，因此英語會話對她來說並不困難，在大學時曾參加過「東洋大學小姐選拔」，一路殺進準決賽，之後也有參加過「Miss Action 2017」和「Miss FLASH 2018」等選美比賽，是被認證過的高顏值。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/085642_ce5c53269dfdc60f052e0fea4a3b9b87.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F085642_ce5c53269dfdc60f052e0fea4a3b9b87.png&h=05c8bf02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n憑藉著漂亮的臉蛋、傲人的身材以及173的大長腿，上福雪從事了模特兒的行業，在因緣際會之下又加入了職業摔角界，讓她成為身兼寫真模特的女子摔角手，擁有這樣雙重身分的反差形象，讓網友們都身陷她的魅力之中，直呼：「還沒開始看比賽就先噴鼻血了啦！」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/085732_f661648c75803471f0c057c0bd6420ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F085732_f661648c75803471f0c057c0bd6420ca.png&h=8d1b866a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b69ccd31e0ac016cbf48066be7ea185740557f99","tid":881992,"uid":164932,"like":178,"dislike":6,"score":172,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:59:19.000Z","msg":"快點撻我落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504358d9f39bd4a799d05bf84a4a5c86b44d608a","tid":881992,"uid":197640,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28e45634ad49b4e38c75d2d84e7cc46b4d0fdc0","tid":881992,"uid":127929,"like":7,"dislike":13,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:02:09.000Z","msg":"應該幾好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3fc2a344ba744562b0ea1efe229a5f220ad572","tid":881992,"uid":59898,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6eb0b60c1a5d7f11bc1106e38ec593ea9c8639","tid":881992,"uid":61974,"like":125,"dislike":8,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/4/3046/2716660653_0369c46393.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F4%2F3046%2F2716660653_0369c46393.jpg&h=77084b88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbf7892dd9159cc88be6924c8d3627dd5a152853","tid":881992,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:04:22.000Z","msg":"想在床上面比佢夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ebab58e505a26f009f6ca2076e75231f2785a5","tid":881992,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,